#5724
@@yWestern Approach Road@@N~
In Western Approach Road, practical survival and legal formality occupy the same narrow ground.  Tariff stones near the lane edge show three generations of overwritten conversion notes.  Canvas shade snaps in the wind while clerks call out loads and witnesses answer by rote.  Repair benches, harness hooks, and provision racks keep this quarter in a perpetual state of departure.  The available lines north and east force a deliberate tradeoff in risk and pace.  Caravans still pause to reset confidence here before committing to the harsher interior spans.
