@@gCairn Tablet Reading Room@@N~
Cairn Tablet Reading Room sits at the intersection of weather and policy, where terrain and procedure have been negotiating for generations.  Small disputes flare and cool quickly, because everyone here knows delay can kill farther east.  Warden paint marks still divide traffic channels even where the original paving has failed.  Even brief stops become procedural: count, inspect, annotate, and release.  From here, movement commits north with little opportunity to hedge the decision.
