#5775
@@gWind-Scoured Span@@N~
Wind-Scoured Span carries the Reach's long memory, with each era leaving traces instead of clean replacements.  The fast line rewards confidence only when paired with discipline and route memory.  A single bad angle of light can erase the safe path and expose hidden breaks.  Kite shadows cross the flats in long arcs that travelers mistake for moving landmarks.  The available lines east and west force a deliberate tradeoff in risk and pace.
